name: User Management
description: This reporting module lists audit information on all user management actions.

reports.name: Users password changes
reports.description: This Report provides audit information on all the user based password changes in the selected period of time.

reports.name: Password changes attempted by an administrator
reports.description: This report provides audit information on the passwords that an administrator changed in the selected time period.

reports.name: Created users
reports.description: This report provides audit information on all created users in the selected time period.

reports.name: Deleted users
reports.description: This report provides audit information on all deleted users in the selected time period.

reports.name: Enabled users
reports.description: This report provides audit information on all enabled users in the selected time period.

reports.name: Disabled users
reports.description: This report provides audit Information on all disabled users in the selected time period.

reports.name: Locked out users
reports.description: This report provides audit Information on all locked out users in the selected time period.

reports.name: Unlocked users
reports.description: This Report provides Audit information on all the frequently unlocked users in the selected period.

reports.name: Changed user account
reports.description: This report provides audit Information on all changed user's accounts in the selected time period.

reports.name: Active Directory-All users
reports.description: This report provide audit information over all users

reports.name: Active Directory-Inactive users
reports.description: This report provide audit information over all inactive users

reports.name: Active Directory-Users with password never expire
reports.description: This report provide audit information over all users with password never expire

reports.name: Active Directory-Password expired users
reports.description: This report provide audit information over all users with password expired
